data.description: Lovely low maintenance home in the heart of Hampstead.  This townhouse boasts 4 generous sized bedrooms with 2 full baths and a half in the desirable Topsail School district.  As you walk in, a formal dining room is on the right and to the left is the staircase leading to the 2nd floor. From both main hallway and dining room you can enter the kitchen with lots of counterspace & cabinets and stainless appliances.  Living room with corner fireplace and sliding glass doors lead to the tranquil sunroom overlooking the large private backyard.  The master suite is complete with double vanity, stand-up shower, soaking tub and walk-in closet. 3 bedrooms upstairs with a full bath and large walk-in attic for all your storage needs and a loft area ideal for a play area, den or home office.  Enjoy the peaceful and nicely landscaped backyard with oversized stone patio perfect for outdoor grilling.  The HOA covers wind & hail insurance for the exterior including the roof and yard maintenance/landscaping.
